S3E1.title: The One with Ross's New Girlfriend
S3E1.des:
Rachel waits at the airport for Ross, not
                knowing he is returning from China with his new girlfriend, Julie. Phoebe gives Monica an awful
                haircut.

S3E2.title: The One with the Breast Milk
S3E2.des:
The guys are uncomfortable with the thought of
                Carol's breast milk, while Rachel is upset by Monica's growing friendship with Julie.

S3E3.title: The One Where Heckles Dies
S3E3.des:
After Mr. Heckles dies and leaves all his
                belongings to Monica and Rachel, Chandler discovers he has eerie similarities with the late
                eccentric man.

S3E4.title: The One with Phoebe's Husband
S3E4.des:
Phoebe has married a gay Canadian ice dancer to
                help him get his green card.

S3E5.title: The One with Five Steaks and an Eggplant
S3E5.des:
Income issues divide the friends. Monica, Ross
                and Chandler have money; Phoebe, Rachel and Joey don't.

S3E6.title: The One with the Baby on the Bus
S3E6.des:
Chandler and Joey lose Ross's son while checking
                out women on a bus.

S3E7.title: The One Where Ross Finds Out
S3E7.des:
A drunken Rachel calls Ross and reveals her
                feelings for him on his answering machine. Now, Ross must make a decision between her and Julie.

S3E8.title: The One with the List
S3E8.des:
Joey and Chandler try to help Ross with his
                decision to date Julie or Rachel by making a list of the pros and cons of each.

S3E9.title: The One with Phoebe's Dad
S3E9.des:
In this Christmas episode, Phoebe tries to track
                down her real father.

S3E10.title: The One with Russ
S3E10.des:
Rachel is dating a guy named Russ, and is blind
                to his uncanny resemblance to Ross.

S3E11.title: The One with the Lesbian Wedding
S3E11.des:
Monica caters the wedding of Ross's ex-wife and
                her lesbian lover. Rachel learns that her mom and dad are getting a divorce.

S3E12.title: The One After the Super Bowl: Part 1
S3E12.des:
Ross travels to San Diego to visit Marcel, his
                monkey. Joey is stalked by a fan of his daytime drama. First of a two-part episode.

S3E13.title: The One After the Super Bowl: Part 2
S3E13.des:
Rachel and Monica compete for the affections of
                Jean-Claude Van Damme. Ross and Marcel go on a tour of the city. Second of a two-part episode.

S3E14.title: The One with the Prom Video
S3E14.des:
Monica and Rachel's prom video reveals Monica's
                former girth, Rachel's former nose and the way Ross has always felt about Rachel.

S3E15.title: The One Where Ross and Rachel...You Know
S3E15.des:
Ross and Rachel finally sleep together. Monica
                becomes infatuated with one of her parents' friends, for whom she caters a party.

S3E16.title: The One Where Joey Moves Out
S3E16.des:
After having a fight with Chandler, Joey moves
                out. Monica's father finds out that Monica is dating his best friend.

S3E17.title: The One Where Eddie Moves In
S3E17.des:
Joey considers moving back in with Chandler, but
                Chandler has a new roommate.

S3E18.title: The One Where Dr. Ramoray Dies
S3E18.des:
Joey's soap opera character gets dropped down an
                elevator shaft after Joey brags about writing his own lines.

S3E19.title: The One Where Eddie Won't Go
S3E19.des:
Chandler demands that his bizarre new roommate,
                Eddie, move out ... but Eddie won't go.

S3E20.title: The One Where Old Yeller Dies
S3E20.des:
Phoebe's world view is shattered when she learns
                how "Old Yeller" really ends.

S3E21.title: The One with the Bullies
S3E21.des:
Two bullies eject Chandler and Ross from Central
                Perk. Phoebe meets a brother she never knew she had.

S3E22.title: The One with the Two Parties
S3E22.des:
Complications ensue when Rachel's estranged
                parents show up at the surprise party that the gang planned for her.

S3E23.title: The One with the Chicken Pox
S3E23.des:
Phoebe catches chicken pox from the baby, just
                as her ex-boyfriend returns on shore leave from the Navy.

S3E24.title: The One with Barry and Mindy's Wedding
S3E24.des:
Rachel agrees to be the maid of honor at her
                ex-fiancé's wedding.

year:
Rachel gets jealous of Ross's new girlfriend, Monica
            dates an older man, and Joey stars on a soap opera as the hit sitcom hits its stride in Season 2.
about:
